<item>
            <title>[LU-4991] Test failure on test suite sanity, subtest test_56s</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4991</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a9564aa0-d154-11e3-96e1-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/a9564aa0-d154-11e3-96e1-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_56s failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&quot;/usr/bin/lfs find -stripe-count 8 -type f /mnt/lustre/d56s.sanitys&quot; wrong: found 4, expected 12&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 56s&lt;/p&gt;</description>
